Detailed Description

template<class T>
class HashMap< T >

Simple HashMap class.

This implementation uses the separate chaining algorithm for handling collisions. Keys can only be char arrays, and must be null terminated. String literals are expected. Hashing is calculated based on the characters in the string.

HashMap is best used with SPtrs, see ArrayList documentation for more details

LinkedList
